    "For n = 500, the experiment is repeated 20 times.",
    "In total, 81, 000 finetuned BERT and GPT-2 models were evaluated.",
    "One source of variance is intentionally introduced: the subsample splits, as explained in §4.4.",
    "The other source of variance is inherent: the added linear layer to perform classification is initialized with random weights.",
    "We will not assess any particular hypothesis about the role of causality."
